<div>
<p>
<measure quantity="9" unit="months">
<num value="9">九</num>月</measure>
<num value="4">丁卯</num>
<pc>，</pc>太宗禦朝元殿<pc>，</pc>陳列如元會儀<pc>，</pc>帝袞冕<pc>，</pc>設黃麾仗及宮縣之樂於庭<pc>，</pc>
